latestPosts.caption:
Sitting here today feels surreal 🥹 From the little boy who sat in front of the TV dreaming of a day like this, to now being on the screen! It’s a feeling I can’t put into words. I’ve fallen, failed, doubted myself, and almost given up more times than I can count, but I didn’t stop. I kept pushing, and now I’m here.

This might seem like a small achievement to many, but to me, it’s a moment of pure pride. It’s proof that dreams do come true when you fight for them.

A part of me aches because I wish my dad was here to witness this moment. I hope he’s watching from somewhere and smiling with pride. I am making your wife proud alright? This one’s for him and for the little Ronak who dared to dream big and who never gave up, and for everyone who believed in me along the way. 

Thank you for being part of this journey. This is just the beginning, and I couldn’t be more excited for what’s ahead. #engaged #rokayadhoka @jiohotstar @engagedofficial
